            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "The `ocaml_interface` highlights are provided by nvim-treesitter.\r\nThe filetype is not set automatically because Vim uses `ocaml` for both.\r\nYou can add an autocmd to your config or submit an issue/PR to Vim.",
